{
  "texts": [
    "Implementation DetailsBackbone For context matching branch, we explore four 3D-CNN backbones as V-Network, i.e., C3D [149], R(2+1)D [150], R3D [80], [151], and S3D [152] to extract video representations.",
    "Moreover, we adopt R2D-10 as I-Network to extract features from I-frame.",
    "For pose prediction branch, we utilize 1D-CNN-based CGAN for pose prediction.",
    "In addition, R3D-based TGAN v2 is leveraged in video generating branch.",
    "It should be noted that during inference, the major computation cost is from video representation extraction network which is mainly determined by various 3D-CNN backbones."
  ]
}